1. Overview

The purpose of the logical model is to design the complete data structure of the SmartBlood system.
This includes entities, attributes, relationships, normalization (up to 3NF), and BI-oriented considerations.

The model ensures data integrity, eliminates redundancy, and supports future analytical needs.

 2. Identified Entities

Based on the business process (Phase II), the following entities are required:

DONOR

DONATION_APPOINTMENT

BLOOD_COLLECTION

LAB_TEST

BLOOD_UNIT

BLOOD_STOCK

HOSPITAL

BLOOD_REQUEST

TRANSFUSION

AUDIT_LOG
